       "    TiO2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " nanoparticle described in the paper:<br>E. G. Brandt, L. Agosta and A.P.Lyubartsev, &quot; Reactive wetting properties  of \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    TiO2\n",
       "    <span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 0.5rem\">MOL</span>\n",
       "</mark>\n",
       " nanoparticles predicted by ab initio molecular dynamics simulations&quot;, Nanoscale, 8, 13385-13398 (2016) DOI: 10.1039/c6nr02791a<br>The trajectories are saved in the .xtc format, and initial structures with specification of atom types are given in the .pdb format.<br>The name of each file contains brief information about the simulated system:<br>\n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
