       "</mark>\n",
       " Protein, and in-silico mutations, under the influence of moderate external electric fields. The final structures of some of the simulations were used to perform in-silico docking with \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    ACE2 receptor\n",
