      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_20359967.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Mebendazole_s_Conformational_Space_and_Its_Predicted_Binding_to_Human_Heat-Shock_Protein_90/20359967)\n",
