       "<span class=\"tex2jax_ignore\"><div class=\"entities\" style=\"line-height: 2.5; direction: ltr\">research data supporting &quot;Revealing the organization of catalytic sequence-defined oligomers via combined molecular dynamics simulations and network analysis&quot;<br>This repository contains all the data generated and analyzed including the starting structures, the input files, the trajectory files, the output data from cpptraj and network analyses, and in-house scripts used to prepare the network and module files shown in the paper &quot;Revealing the organization of catalytic sequence-defined oligomers via combined molecular dynamics simulations and network analysis&quot; published in Journal of Chemical Information and Modeling (DOI: 10.1021/acs.jcim.2c00101). </div></span>"
