      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_3467309.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Structural_Studies_of_Supramolecular_G_Quadruplexes_Formed_from_8_Aryl-2_-deoxyguanosine_Derivatives/3467309)\n",
