      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_22203473.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Extension_of_the_TraPPE_Force_Field_for_Battery_Electrolyte_Solvents/22203473)\n",
