      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2271034.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/First_Principles_Simulations_of_the_Initial_Phase_of_Self_Aggregation_of_a_Cyanine_Dye_Structure_and_Optical_Spectra/2271034)\n",
