      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2178850.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Two_Level_Spatial_Modulation_of_Vibronic_Conductance_in_Conjugated_Oligophenylenes_on_Boron_Nitride/2178850)\n",
