       "<span class=\"tex2jax_ignore\"><div class=\"entities\" style=\"line-height: 2.5; direction: ltr\">Aldeghi et al. Files for absolute free energy calculations in \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #ffffba; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
