      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2020311.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/An_Extension_and_Further_Validation_of_an_All_Atomistic_Force_Field_for_Biological_Membranes/2020311)\n",
