       " [2]. The files (xtc and mdp) with '_dc' suffix are simulated with dispersion correction applied to both energy and pressure whereas the files without this suffix do not use this correction.<br>This data is used in the project &quot;Matching lipid force fields with NMR data&quot;, see: http://nmrlipids.blogspot.fi <br>[1] J.P. Ulmschneider &amp; M.B. Ulmschneider, United Atom Lipid Parameters for Combination with the Optimized Potentials for Liquid Simulations All-Atom Force Field, JCTC 2009, 5(7), 1803–1813<br>[2] http://lipidbook.bioch.ox.ac.uk/package/show/id/52.html</div></span>"
