      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_21806756.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/LassoHTP_A_High-Throughput_Computational_Tool_for_Lasso_Peptide_Structure_Construction_and_Modeling/21806756)\n",
