      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_6874760.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Machine_Learning_Adaptive_Basis_Sets_for_Efficient_Large_Scale_Density_Functional_Theory_Simulation/6874760)\n",
