      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_3470993.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Structural_Characterization_of_Alkylsilane_and_Fluoroalkylsilane_Self-Assembled_Monolayers_on_SiO_sub_2_sub_by_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulations/3470993)\n",
