      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2276194.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Free_Energy_Calculation_of_Nanodiamond_Membrane_Association_The_Effect_of_Shape_and_Surface_Functionalization/2276194)\n",
