       "</mark>\n",
       " (=36.85°C).-The two images in the main folder refers to the docked structures before MD simulation.-The file all_centroids.pse contains the frames representing the centroid of the subsequent MD simulation for each docking cluster.-Each archive contains the centroid in PDB format, the starting frame of the simulation in GRO format and the compressed trajectory in XTC format. In the directory &quot;other_files&quot; there are other data generated during the simulation, i.e. heatmap representing the contact frequency between the ligand atoms and the ones belonging to the homology model.</div></span>"
