      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_11808321.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Quantum_Mechanics_Molecular_Mechanics_Density_Functional_Theory_Simulations_of_the_Optical_Properties_Fingerprinting_the_Ligand-Binding_of_Pentameric_Formyl_Thiophene_Acetic_Acid_in_Amyloid-_1_42_/11808321)\n",
