       "</mark>\n",
       " ( DOI: 10.1021/acs.jctc.8b00765 ), are maintained using restrained dummy particles that repel lipid acyl chains<br>All input and output files are provided for each simulation, and the cpt files allow to extend the simulations. The top, itp (in TOP.tar archive), mdp, and ndx files are common for each simulation.<br>The simulations have been used in DOI: 10.1101/2020.09.23.310086.</div></span>"
