      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_8292209.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Interdependent_Electronic_Structure_Protonation_and_Solvatization_of_Aqueous_2_Thiopyridone/8292209)\n",
