      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_19657472.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Recognition_and_Binding_of_RsmE_to_an_AGGAC_Motif_of_RsmZ_Insights_from_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulations/19657472)\n",
