      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_7370684.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Stereospecific_1_3_H_Transfer_of_Indenols_Proceeds_via_Persistent_Ion-Pairs_Anchored_by_NH__Interactions/7370684)\n",
