      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_16712908.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Just_Add_Water_Modulating_the_Structure-Derived_Acidity_of_Catalytic_Hexameric_Resorcinarene_Capsules/16712908)\n",
