       " can read it.)<br>The folder &quot;36bundle&quot; contains input files for creating the initial configuration of the bundle with 36 chains in a maze configuration, namely 36bundle.sh reads 1chain.xyz to make the coordinate file 36bundle.xyz. Further, nvt00.in is the initial \n",
