      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_7691966.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Addressing_Polarization_Phenomena_in_Molecular_Machines_Containing_Transition_Metal_Ions_with_an_Additive_Force_Field/7691966)\n",
