      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2018634.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Derivation_and_Systematic_Validation_of_a_Refined_All_Atom_Force_Field_for_Phosphatidylcholine_Lipids/2018634)\n",
