      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_2478628.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Adsorption_Behavior_of_Hydrophobin_Proteins_on_Polydimethylsiloxane_Substrates/2478628)\n",
