      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_19082291.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Importance_of_Three-Body_Problems_and_Protein_Protein_Interactions_in_Proteolysis-Targeting_Chimera_Modeling_Insights_from_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulations/19082291)\n",
