      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_14428978.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Mechanism_of_Glycans_Modulating_Cholesteryl_Ester_Transfer_Protein_Unveiled_by_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulation/14428978)\n",
