      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_7586417.json: https://figshare.com/articles/dataset/Molecular_modelling_of_HPV_E6_protein_reveal_new_potential_inhibitors_against_high-risk_Human_Papillomavirus_Supporting_Information/7586417)\n",
