      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_19652739.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Expanding_the_Accessible_Chemical_Space_of_SIRT2_Inhibitors_through_Exploration_of_Binding_Pocket_Dynamics/19652739)\n",
