      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_3426170.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Combining_Linear-Scaling_DFT_with_Subsystem_DFT_in_Born_Oppenheimer_and_Ehrenfest_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulations_From_Molecules_to_a_Virus_in_Solution/3426170)\n",
