      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_19102457.json: https://tandf.figshare.com/articles/dataset/LNA-induced_dynamic_stability_in_a_therapeutic_aptamer_insights_from_molecular_dynamics_simulations/19102457)\n",
