      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_12661589.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Comprehensive_Computational_Analysis_Exploring_the_Formation_of_Caprolactam-Based_Deep_Eutectic_Solvents_and_Their_Applications_in_Natural_Gas_Desulfurization/12661589)\n",
