      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_20334621.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Modeling_Gd_sup_3_sup_Complexes_for_Molecular_Dynamics_Simulations_Toward_a_Rational_Optimization_of_MRI_Contrast_Agents/20334621)\n",
