       ")<br>Raw data of molecular dynamics simulations of regulatory ACT domain monomer.<br>binding.zip: simulation starting from 21 monomer conformations with 19 Phe ligand <br>bound.zip: simulation starting from monomer with bound Phe ligand<br>monomer_only.zip: simulation starting from 21 monomer conformations simulation<br>Simulation setup files are also included in each folder. Adaptive sampling data are also included in monomer and binding simulations.<br>Details can be found in this paper:<br>Yunhui Ge, Elias Borne, Shannon Stewart, Michael R. Hansen, Emilia C. Arturo, Eileen K. Jaffe and Vincent A. Voelz. Simulation of the regulatory ACT domain of human \n",
