       "</mark>\n",
       ".<br>Pressure coupling: 'Berendsen' [J. Chem. Phys. 81 3684 (1984)] with xy and z coupled separately at p = 1.0 bar.<br>Electrostatics: PME [J. Chem. Phys. 98 10089 (1993); J. Chem. Phys. 103 8577 (1995)], real-space cutoff at 1.0 nm.<br>Van der Waals: Truncated at 1.0 nm.<br>Constraints: Covalent bond lengths in lipids using LINCS [J. Comput. Chem. 18 1463 (1997)], in \n",
       "<mark class=\"entity\" style=\"background: #bae1ff; padding: 0.45em 0.6em; margin: 0 0.25em; line-height: 1; border-radius: 0.35em;\">\n",
       "    water\n",
