     "text": [
      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_11343020.json: https://iastate.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Molecular_Dynamic_Simulation_data_of_compensatory_mutations_in_Bruton_s_Tyrosine_Kinase/11343020)\n",
