      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_4748350.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Extension_of_the_Highly_Mobile_Membrane_Mimetic_to_Transmembrane_Systems_through_Customized_i_in_Silico_i_Solvents/4748350)\n",
