      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_16410502.json: https://tandf.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Determining_structure_and_action_mechanism_of_LBF14_by_molecular_simulation/16410502)\n",
