      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n",
      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_12986024.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Rigorous_Computational_Study_Reveals_What_Docking_Overlooks_Double_Trouble_from_Membrane_Association_in_Protein_Kinase_C_Modulators/12986024)\n",
