      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_12312368.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Small_Changes_in_Hydration_Determine_Cephalosporinase_Activity_of_OXA-48_Lactamases/12312368)\n",
