      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_12168798.json: https://plos.figshare.com/articles/dataset/Dataflow_programming_for_the_analysis_of_molecular_dynamics_with_AViS_an_analysis_and_visualization_software_application/12168798)\n",
