      "VISUALIZATION OF ENTITIES (figshare_7865144.json: https://acs.figshare.com/articles/dataset/The_Necessity_of_d_Thr_in_the_New_Antibiotic_Teixobactin_A_Molecular_Dynamics_Study/7865144)\n",
