       "<span class=\"tex2jax_ignore\"><div class=\"entities\" style=\"line-height: 2.5; direction: ltr\">Raw data for: Cell-free biosynthesis combined with deep learning accelerates de novo-development of antimicrobial peptides<br>This repository contains data related to &quot;Cell-free biosynthesis combined with deep learning accelerates de novo-development of antimicrobial peptides&quot; by Pandi et al.<br>Included are molecular dynamics parameter files, initial structures after system equilibration and production trajectories. For simulations of \n",
